f] SCOPED Instant Coffee Time right now on WABC [Description by Uncle Ricky] Again there is even less of Harry Harrison in Part 3 of this aircheck from March 11 1975 There s plenty of other things however often overlapping each other The most uncomfortable are the jingle layovers over intros that step on song vocals and other jingles! But this was WABC this was 1975 and this rushed approach to their classic format was the answer to the enemy army of FM More Music radio There are a couple of Harry coffee jingles and a couple of coffee sponsors and WABC is really pushing coffee in the last hour leading into a few seconds of Hello Love! Ron Lundy Following the closing coffee jingle New York newsman John Meagher returns with a WABC newscast followed by Don Gardner on the ABC Contemporary Network [combtn gif] [rew gif] Return to the Repository MORE GOLDEN GIFTS [wwwrrcom gif] Reel Top 40 Radio Repository ©1996 2015 REELRADIO INC');
