 him say creme sandwich cookies and Nuts and Nutmeats? Awesome spots too I want that Mustang and what about the Suzuki jingle in which nothing rhymes? It s an absolutely elegant piece of production as is the Oscar Meyer jingle and the GM Mark of Excellence spot at the end of the hour [combtn gif] [rew gif] Return to the Repository [dotgold gif] [g250 gif] up to 10Khz (32 Kbps) PLAY The Real Don Steele KHJ Los Angeles March 28 1968 4 5PM (48:48) This Exhibit scoped (14:23) [tinyscoped png] and it controls howling feedback unless you dig it 93 KHJ BOSS 30 ONLINE [iplay gif] You know The Real Don Steele is in the show business capital of the world when he opens this 4PM hour with a spot for a microphone! This is the second restored hour from Thursday March 28 1968 Still there s ten minutes missing from this hour best guess: a long afternoon drive newscast Twice in this hour where original content was unavailable Johnny Mann jingles filled the gap [combtn gif] [rew gif] Return to the Repository [dotgold gif] [g250 gif] up to 10Khz (20 7 Kbps) PLAY The Real Don Steele KHJ Los Angeles March 29 1968 (57:10) Don t touch me I m red hot! It s a Fractious Friday and this aircheck of The Real Don Steele from 3 to 6PM on March 29 1968 is a Boss delight (especially at 20 7 Kbps G2!) This one was taped in the KHJ studios and the technical quality is superb You ll hear a rare Big 93 jingle a plethora of 1960 s beer spots Dino Desi & Billy (for RC Cola) and a teaser promo for the Quicksilver jackpot the biggest cash prize ever And despite the incredible energy expended by Steele in the first two hours he tops himself in the 5PM hour [combtn gif] [rew gif] Return to the Repository [dotgold gif] [g250 gif] TOP STREAM 32Kbps (14 5 Khz) PLAY The Real Don Steele KHJ Los Angeles May 18 1968 (01:01:01) Ray Charles for the Frances Faye underground out there 93 KHJ BOSS 30 ONLINE This partially scoped aircheck of 93/KHJ was recorded on a Scintillating Saturday May 18 1968 from approximately 